author: smishura
msg: Remove call to 'error-notify' macrodef and macrodef itself.
It doesn't make sense to try to send notification again if previous attempt failed.
Most probably the second attempt will fail for the same reason as the first one.
But the second attempt causes the build to fail as it is not inside try-catch block.
